        <div type="letter">
            <div type="text">
                <opener>
                    <placeName>12 Upper Gower St<hi rend="superscript">t</hi>.—</placeName>
                    <salute>My dear M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Babbage</salute>
                </opener>
                <div type="transcription">
                     
<p>Will you have the kindness to excuse me, once again asking your permission to bring with M<hi rend="superscript">rs</hi>. Darwin and myself, to your party on Saturday Evening, a relative of ours, Miss Allen<ref target="#foot.f1"/> of Cresselly, who is staying with us.—</p>
<p>Believe me | Very truly yours | Chas. Darwin <lb resp="#mjhawkins"/> Thursday.—</p> 
                </div>
            </div>
                <div type="tnotes">
                    <note xml:id="tnote.n1">1.2 to your] ‘to’ <hi rend="italic">over</hi> ‘a’; <hi rend="italic">before del</hi> ‘relat’</note>
                </div>

        </div>

        

        

        <div type="footnotes">
            <note xml:id="foot.f1">Frances (Fanny) Allen.</note>
        </div>        
            
